    title: { rendered: "How to Build a Winning Digital Marketing Plan" },
    content: {
      rendered:
        "<body>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<h2>Goals</h2>\nCover Marketing\nSEO Marketing\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<h2>Engagement Strategies</h2>\n<h2>Skillset to improve\nYour Company Brand</h2>\n<h2>Improving your company brand through digital marketing involves a combination of skills that cover various aspects of marketing, design, content creation, and data analysis.</h2>\n\nDefine your target audience and goals.\nResearch competitors and market trends.\nEstimate costs for each channel and campaign\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<h2>Digital Marketing</h2>\n<h2>Learn to foster interactions and build relationships with your audience.\n</h2>\n\n\n\n\n<h2>SEO Optimization</h2>\n<h2> Learn techniques for optimizing website content and building backlinks.</h2>\n\n\n\n\n<h2>Product Research</h2>\n<h2> Track website performance and user behavior to make informed decisions.</h2>\n\n\n\n\n<h2>Web Development</h2>\n<h2> Understand the basics of web design to optimize your company website.</h2>\n\n</body>",
      protected: false,
    },
    excerpt: {
      rendered:
        "<p>Creating a successful digital marketing plan is essential for businesses and marketers to thrive in today\u2019s competitive online landscape. A well-structured plan not only ensures clear goals and objectives but also helps align resources, tools, and strategies for maximum impact.</p>\n",
      protected: false,
    },
